---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---
<Base title="Privacy Policy — Tetora" lang="en">
  <nav style="padding:50px 20px 0;max-width:780px;margin:0 auto;font-size:13px;color:var(--muted)">
    <a href="/" style="color:var(--muted)">&larr; Tetora</a> / Privacy Policy
  </nav>
  <div style="max-width:780px;margin:0 auto;padding:48px 20px 40px;line-height:1.8;color:var(--fg)">
    <h1 style="font-size:2rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-0.02em;margin-bottom:24px">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p style="color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:32px">Last updated: March 2026</p>

    <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:600;margin:32px 0 12px">Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>Tetora.dev does not collect personal information directly. However, we use third-party services that may collect data automatically:</p>

    <h3 style="font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:600;margin:24px 0 8px">Google Analytics</h3>
    <p>We use Google Analytics (GA4, measurement ID: G-X6YR7HG68N) to understand how visitors interact with our site. Google Analytics collects information such as:</p>
    <ul style="margin:8px 0 16px 24px">
      <li>Pages visited and time spent</li>
      <li>Approximate geographic location (country/city level)</li>
      <li>Device type, browser, and operating system</li>
      <li>Referral source</li>
    </ul>
    <p>This data is aggregated and does not personally identify you. For more information, see <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" style="color:var(--accent)">Google's Privacy Policy</a>.</p>

    <h3 style="font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:600;margin:24px 0 8px">Google AdSense</h3>
    <p>We may display advertisements provided by Google AdSense. Google AdSense uses cookies and similar technologies to serve ads based on your prior visits to this site or other websites. You can opt out of personalized advertising by visiting <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" style="color:var(--accent)">Google Ads Settings</a>.</p>
    <p>Third-party vendors, including Google, use cookies to serve ads based on your prior visits. You may opt out of third-party vendor cookies for personalized advertising by visiting <a href="https://www.aboutads.info/choices/" style="color:var(--accent)">www.aboutads.info</a>.</p>

    <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:600;margin:32px 0 12px">Cookies</h2>
    <p>This site uses cookies set by Google Analytics and Google AdSense. Cookies are small text files stored on your device. They help us analyze site traffic and enable advertising functionality. You can control cookies through your browser settings.</p>

    <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:600;margin:32px 0 12px">Your Rights (GDPR / CCPA)</h2>
    <p>If you are located in the EU/EEA or California, you may have the right to:</p>
    <ul style="margin:8px 0 16px 24px">
      <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
      <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
      <li>Opt out of the sale of personal information (we do not sell data)</li>
      <li>Opt out of personalized advertising</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:600;margin:32px 0 12px">Contact</h2>
    <p>For privacy-related inquiries, please open an issue on our <a href="https://github.com/TakumaLee/Tetora" style="color:var(--accent)">GitHub repository</a>.</p>

    <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:600;margin:32px 0 12px">Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.</p>
  </div>
  <Footer />
</Base>
